===Pronunciation===
*swĕt, /swet/, /swet/

=== Noun ===
'''sweat'''

#[[Fluid]] that exits the [[body]] though [[pore]]s in the [[skin]] usually due to [[physical]] [[stress]] and/or [[high]] [[temperature]]. Regulates body temperature and removes unuseful compounds from the blood circulation.

